{"tid":356577,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"台電員工月領7萬　上班睡3小時再看報下班","createTime":"2017-08-12T07:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T10:04:01.000Z","uid":56533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6f6a2b363697ef4353a9261a6aa0ba278a43ef","tid":356577,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170812/640_968234939161c38084db5fa9a805dbc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170812%2F640_968234939161c38084db5fa9a805dbc6.jpg&h=dad43cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台電公職鐵飯碗，他月領7萬卻睡覺、看報，同事看不下去。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，台電台東區營運處檢修課一名服務超過40年、月領逾7萬元的職員，常在上班時間睡覺、看報，叫他工作常以「不會」、「忘記」推託。本月10日他趴睡從下午1時睡到4時，起來再看報，看在工作到滿身大汗的同事眼底，心裡不是滋味。<br />\n<br />\n營運處表示，該名員工曾因身體不適緊急送醫，因需長期服藥控制病情致精神不佳。因未達退休65歲年齡，若其家庭經濟狀況允許，將建議他請假在家休養，若有上班需求，將調動到其身體狀況可以負荷的職務。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170812/1180742/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170812%2F1180742%2F&d=1P3sp5kVsOiNtwDcUNde88P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=03facc11\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170812/1180742/</a>"},{"pid":"4dd49e3c7d3c5bedd2982cdebd763e8ef2db294c","tid":356577,"uid":65072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:59:11.000Z","msg":"香港班舊制廢老公務員咪一鳩樣"},{"pid":"81a73f745d225b0e1b3ba1c80610e7b255e2a083","tid":356577,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:03:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港班舊制廢老公務員咪一鳩樣</blockquote><br />\n然後呢?<br />\n你又可以點做?"},{"pid":"876478faa6dec6e49f804285f6704db788c58db1","tid":356577,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:08:19.000Z","msg":"番工本來就應該幾個鐘咁番<br />\n訓教都應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\